    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Blessed are ye that hunger now,.... Not only suffer hunger and thirst in a literal sense, in this present life, but who have hunger and thirst in a spiritual sense, after righteousness and eternal life, as in ",
