      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "blessed are ye that weep now; under afflictions and pressures of life, and mourn for sin, their own, and others: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "for ye shall laugh; be filled with spiritual joy and pleasure, and be comforted with the consolations of the Spirit; See Gill on Matthew 5:4. ",
